[[Image:Middle-earth Calendar 1998 (Finnish).jpg|thumb]]

'''Middle-earth Calendar 1998''' was produced by the [[Finnish Tolkien Society]] and includes pen and ink illustrations by [[Sari Luoto-Tudeer]], [[Rudi Airisto]], [[Sami Vähä-Aho]], [[Päivi Tienari]], and [[Lovissa Mustonen]]. The calendar also includes brief notes on the illustrators and information about the society.

* Dimensions: 11 11/16 x 8 1/4 inches
* Stapled
* No hanging hole
